  <ul class="accordion">
    <li>
      <a href="#" class="toggle">WHAT IS THINQ.TV ?</a>
      <div class="inner">
        <div id="content-container">
          <p>ThinQ.tv is like a Zoom meeting or Google Hangout, except that people can drop in to the Conversation from the home page schedule instead of having to be invited with a link. Please browse the current schedule and drop in to any of the Conversations posted. You may also post your own Conversation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
