            <p>OR go to a Conversation on the ThinQ.tv mobile site. Scroll down to where the Conversation viewer is embedded. There will be a link there to install JITSI Meet on your phone. If JITSI Meet is already installed, it will automatically take you to the ThinQtv chatroom.</p>
